title: Redesign Rev1 Physibles
description:
A collection of physibles that allow the hybridisation of household appliances, altering their function and meaning. Created and distributed as part of the curriculum for the Redesign Elective Course at the Willem de Kooning University, Rotterdam, NL.

What's included:
-preview selection (see 'preview' folder)
-3d model files (.stls, .obj and or .skp) and/or lasercut vector graphics
-CURA printer settings
-sketches, tests
-photos of the final print.
-projects separated per folder


Please read the readme.pdf included in every folder for the license regarding
copying, modifiying, redistribution.

Most descriptions are in Dutch, but combined with the images you'll figure out what it is. Please feel free tot translate.

Please do not redistribute on commercial websites such as thingiverse, instructables etc. THEY OWN YOU AND YOUR WORK.
